children.name: pmssno
children.description: PMSS ID# - While adding PMSS records abstractors must first pick the Reporting Jurisdiction, then the Year-of-Death. Based on these 2 parameters the Unique PMSS# is automatically generated. Example: If PMSS# is 00230001 the numbers in position 1-2 is Jurisdiction Code (here 00 for NYC), 3-4 is Year in YY (here 23 for 2023); finally, numbers in position 5-8 are the next-sequential Case-ID# for the selected jurisdiction and year starting with 1 (here 0001).
